ed":0},"issue_dependencies_summary":{"blocked_by":0,"total_blocked_by":0,"blocking":0,"total_blocking":0},"body":"I've noticed that handleError and handleFatalError will log the same error twice, with the default configuration of `Monolog\\ErrorHandler::register()`. Here's a simple example:\n## Code\n\n```\nrequire_once('vendor/autoload.php');\n\n$logger = new Monolog\\Logger('test');\n$logger->pushHandler(new Monolog\\Handler\\StreamHandler(STDOUT, Monolog\\Logger::DEBUG));\n\nMonolog\\ErrorHandler::register($logger);\nuser_error('test', E_USER_ERROR);\n```\n## Output\n\n```\n[2015-08-05 11:31:02] test.ERROR: E_USER_ERROR: test {\"code\":256,\"message\":\"test\",\"file\":\"/Users/sminnee/Sites/ss4/test.php\",\"line\":9} []\nPHP Fatal error:  test in /Users/sminnee/Sites/ss4/test.php on line 9\nPHP Stack trace:\nPHP   1. {main}() /Users/sminnee/Sites/ss4/test.php:0\nPHP   2. user_error() /Users/sminnee/Sites/ss4/test.php:9\n\nFatal error: test in /Users/sminnee/Sites/ss4/test.php on line 9\n\nCall Stack:\n    0.0002     226800   1. {main}() /Users/sminnee/Sites/ss4/test.php:0\n    0.0034     674416   2. user_error() /Users/sminnee/Sites/ss4/test.php:9\n\n[2015-08-05 11:31:02] test.ALERT: Fatal Error (E_USER_ERROR): test {\"code\":256,\"message\":\"test\",\"file\":\"/Users/sminnee/Sites/ss4/test.php\",\"line\":9} []\n```\n","closed_by":{"login":"Seldaek","id":183678,"node_id":"MDQ6VXNlcjE4MzY3OA==","avatar_url":"https://avatars.githubusercontent.com/u/183678?v=4","gravatar_id":"","url":"https://api.github.com/users/Seldaek","html_url":"https://github.com/Seldaek","followers_url":"https://api.github.com/users/Seldaek/followers","following_url":"https://api.github.com/users/Seldaek/following{/other_user}","gists_url":"https://api.github.com/users/Seldaek/gists{/gist_id}","starred_url":"https://api.github.com/users/Seldaek/starred{/owner}{/repo}","subscriptions_url":"https://api.github.com/users/Seldaek/subscriptions","organizations_url":"https://api.github.com/users/Se